This template uses ship data modules to display an infobox for the requested ship.

==Example==
 <nowiki>{{EnemyShipInfoKai|name=Standard Carrier Wo-Class|model=Kai Flagship}}</nowiki>

becomes
{{EnemyShipInfoKai|name=Standard Carrier Wo-Class|model=Kai Flagship}}

==Parameters==
The following are the parameters that can be passed.

===name===
The name of the ship, without any suffixes.

===model===
The model of the ship, ie. the suffix. For example, Elite or Flagship.

To specify the base model you can omit model or leave model empty.

